606
00:36:17,720 --> 00:36:18,920
Wang Xingsheng…

607
00:36:19,680 --> 00:36:21,000
Has he gone missing?

608
00:36:22,720 --> 00:36:25,760
He left me a flash drive.

609
00:36:26,520 --> 00:36:27,480
I'm guessing

610
00:36:27,560 --> 00:36:29,840
what's on it will interest you.

611
00:36:29,920 --> 00:36:32,160
And I'll be well compensated.

612
00:36:36,960 --> 00:36:38,040
Stop!

613
00:37:29,560 --> 00:37:31,520
She went that way.

614
00:37:37,880 --> 00:37:38,880
Thank you.

