<i>Remove your item and close the door.</i>

616
00:38:33,080 --> 00:38:36,200
The flash drive's
in a hotel parcel locker.

617
00:38:37,080 --> 00:38:39,040
Once your payment clears,

618
00:38:39,120 --> 00:38:41,000
<i>I'll give you the code.</i>

619
00:38:41,080 --> 00:38:42,080
<i>Deal?</i>

620
00:39:07,080 --> 00:39:08,040
Are you alright?

621
00:39:08,120 --> 00:39:09,240
- Did you get hurt?
- I'm fine. Where's the drive?

622
00:39:10,720 --> 00:39:11,840
Right here.

623
00:39:31,040 --> 00:39:33,440
It's empty. There's nothing on it.

624
00:39:33,520 --> 00:39:34,560
I'll call him.

625
00:39:41,560 --> 00:39:45,200
<i>Sorry, the subscriber you dialed</i>
<i>is not available.</i>

626
00:39:45,960 --> 00:39:47,400
Looks like we've been played.

627
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:51,000
Fat Buddha

628
00:39:51,080 --> 00:39:52,520
is always holding something back.

629
00:39:53,960 --> 00:39:54,800
We can't waste time.

630
00:39:55,320 --> 00:39:58,280
Before Li Lingbai finds out
her drive's a fake,

631
00:39:58,800 --> 00:40:00,080
we need to find him.

632
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:10,960
What's wrong?

633
00:40:11,480 --> 00:40:12,680
Are you upset?

634
00:40:13,840 --> 00:40:15,240
No.

635
00:40:15,320 --> 00:40:16,480
Just tired.

